title: BRIEF-Piteco sees minimum payout ratio of 40 pct for FY 2015 dividend
text:
BRIEF-Piteco sees minimum payout ratio of 40 pct for FY 2015 dividend 
Oct 2 Piteco SpA : 
* Sees to distribute FY 2015 dividend 
* Sees minimum payout ratio for FY 2015 dividend of 40 percent
